data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Located in the heart of Alamogordo, surrounded by the calming Sacramento Mountains, this 3 bedroom, 1.75 Bath, 2128 sqft house has SO much to offer. With a .25 of an acre corner lot in a cul-de-sac, you'll have room for all your toys! RV Access with a gated backyard, not to forget the oversized 2-car garage. There are many upgrades outside including a new roof in 2019! Stepping in, you'll be greeted with beautiful hardwood floors and a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The kitchen is gorgeous and easy to take care of quartz countertops (2021). PEX Piping (10/21), Water Softener (2015), new living room windows (10/23), and granite countertops/tile (10/21) are just some of the FEW upgrades inside! The house also has a very usable sunroom for any need. On top of all of this, the sellers are offering a $5,000 Allowance for Paint/Carpet. Did I mention; washer, dryer, refrigerator, artwork, TVs, grill, shed, and firewood all convey? This house will not last long, come check it out today!
